| Variable       | Requerido | Valor Ejemplo                                                     | Descripción              |
| -------------- | --------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| `PROVIDER_URL` | ✅        | `http://localhost:5009`                                           | URL pública del Provider |
| `DATABASE_URL` | ✅        | `postgresql://oidc_user:oidc_password_dev@localhost:5437/oidc_db` | Conexión PostgreSQL      |
| `NODE_ENV`     | ⚠️        | `development`                                                     | Ambiente de ejecución    |
| `PORT`         | ❌        | `8080`                                                            | Puerto interno           |

