## Comandos Útiles

### Verificar Configuración

```bash
cd /Users/r1go/Documents/CODE/APPLICA/Acceleralia/oidc-server
./verify-env.sh
```

### Crear Archivos desde Ejemplos

```bash
# OIDC Provider
cd oidc-server/provider && cp .env.example .env

# OIDC Backend
cd oidc-server/backend && cp .env.example .env

# Write-mvp API
cd Write-mvp/apps/api && cp .env.dev.example .env.dev

# Write-mvp Web
cd Write-mvp/apps/web && cp .env.dev.example .env.dev
```

### Verificar Cliente OIDC en Base de Datos

```bash
# Conectar a PostgreSQL de oidc-server
psql -h localhost -p 5437 -U oidc_user -d oidc_db

# Verificar cliente
SELECT client_id, client_name, redirect_uris, post_logout_redirect_uris, is_active
FROM oidc_clients
WHERE client_id = 'writehub-client';
```

### Verificar Servicios

```bash
# OIDC Server
curl http://localhost:5009/.well-known/openid-configuration

# Write-mvp API
curl http://localhost:5008/health

# Write-mvp Web
curl http://localhost:3010/
```

